# Lab

Sandbox/test environment config for {{PROJECT_NAME}}: hosts, VMs, containers, fixtures. Meant to be torn down and rebuilt - nothing here is precious.

## File types
- Provisioning scripts (`Build-*`, `New-*`, `provision-*`)
- Inventory/manifest files (`<thing>-inventory_<date>.json|csv`)
- Image/ISO/container manifests with version + hash

## Rules
- Environment creation is repeatable from one command + parameters file.
- Images/ISOs tracked by version + hash. Stale ones archived, not deleted.
- Every build produces a manifest of what was created.
- No long-lived resources. If something needs persistence, it isn't lab.
- No large binaries in this folder - keep a path reference; binaries live elsewhere.

